method.abstract: Updates the picture contained by the 2D Picture Representation Reference.

class.abstract: Interface dedicated to Logical 2D Pictures collection management.

method.abstract: Retrieves the number of 2D Pictures associated to this Logical Reference.

method.abstract: Retrieves the collection of 2D Pictures associated to this Logical Reference.

class.name: CATILogInstance
class.abstract: Interface designating a Logical Instance.

method.abstract: Connects two instances of logical systems together.

method.abstract: Retrieves the Logical Ports exposing at the upper level a specific port of this instance of logical system.

method.abstract: Retrieves the instances of sibling logical systems connected to this instance of logical system.

method.abstract: Retrieves the Logical Reference which aggregates this Logical Instance.

method.abstract: Retrieves the instanciated Logical Reference.

method.abstract: Retrieves the number of Logical Instances aggregated by this Logical Reference.

method.abstract: Retrieves the collection of instances aggregated by this Logical Reference.

method.abstract: Removes the given instance that is aggregated by this Logical Reference.

class.name: CATILogMuxDemuxReference

enum.name: CommunicationType

class.name: CATILogPort

method.name: GetTypeInstance
method.abstract: Retrieves the Logical Type Instance associated to this Logical Port.

method.name: RemoveType
method.abstract: Removes the Logical Type associated to this Logical Port.

method.abstract: Sets the direction of this Logical Port.

method.abstract: Sets the Logical Type associated to this Logical Port.
